articles.description: Matt Mobley scored 30 points and grabbed nine rebounds, Jaylen Adams added 26 points with five assists and four steals and St. Bonaventure beat La Salle 79-68 on Tuesday night for its first seven-game Atlantic 10 winning streak in program history.
articles.headline: St. Bonaventure wins 7th straight A-10 game for 1st time

articles.description: Jaelen Sanford scored 21 points on 6-of-9 shooting and Tre'Shaun Fletcher had 17 points and eight rebounds to help Toledo beat Ohio 82-74 on Tuesday night for its fourth win in a row.
articles.headline: Sanford scores 21, Fletcher 17 as Toledo beats Ohio 82-74

articles.description: Matt Lewis halted a scoring drought, making two free throws in the final seconds, to give James Madison a 62-61 win over UNC Wilmington on Tuesday night.
articles.headline: Lewis sinks late FTs, James Madison takes 62-61 victory

articles.description: Oklahoma's Trae Young cannot connect from behind the arc as the Sooner returns to his hometown to face Big 12 rivals Texas Tech in Lubbock.
articles.headline: Young struggles against Texas Tech

images.caption: Oklahoma's Trae Young cannot connect from behind the arc as the Sooner returns to his hometown to face Big 12 rivals Texas Tech in Lubbock.
images.name: Young struggles against Texas Tech

articles.description: Elijah Minnie tossed in 24 points and James Thompson IV finished with his 18th double-double of the season to help Eastern Michigan hold off Miami (Ohio) 58-57 on Tuesday night.
articles.headline: Eastern Michigan holds off Miami (OH) 58-57

articles.description: Udoka Azubuike scored 19 points, Malik Newman had 17 and 13th-ranked Kansas bounced back from a brutal loss at Baylor by beating Iowa State 83-77 on Tuesday.
articles.headline: No. 13 Kansas holds off Iowa State 83-77

images.caption: Lagerald Vick lobs it to Udoka Azubuike for another alley-oop.
images.name: Azubuike cannot be stopped

videos.description: Deandre Ayton throws down a massive dunk to get the fans cheering and then Rawle Alkins gets the tough layup and-1 to send the crowd into a frenzy.
videos.headline: Ayton and Alkins bring the crowd to a deafening roar

videos.description: Remy Martin reads the cross-court pass perfectly, intercepts it and throws down a huge jam on the other end.
videos.headline: Martin steals and slams for the Sun Devils

videos.description: Remy Martin is feeling it early and knocks down the step-back in front of two Wildcats.
videos.headline: Martin hits deadly step-back jumper

videos.description: Deandre Ayton gets the pass on the inbound and throws down a massive one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Ayton throws down the hammer

videos.description: Deandre Ayton grabs the offensive board and then sends home the ferocious dunk.
videos.headline: Ayton battles through traffic for and-1 hammer dunk

videos.description: Tra Holder decides to pull up and knocks down the long-range three as the Sun Devils try and claw back.
videos.headline: Holder pulls up and drains triple

videos.description: Arizona has pressure in the backcourt, resulting in a turnover to the Sun Devils and Tra Holder immediately drains the jumper to get Arizona State to within a point.
videos.headline: Holder gets ASU to within one

videos.description: Deandre Ayton battles closely with his defender and wins the matchup with a strong layup and the foul.
videos.headline: Ayton powers through for layup and-1

videos.description: Shannon Evans II gets the pass on the fast break and goes up-and-under to get the bucket and-1.
videos.headline: Evans does his best MJ impression with up-and-under layup

videos.description: Arizona grabs the rebound, but could not get a good pass off and Mickey Mitchell kicks it out to Kodi Justice for the three to get the Sun Devils to within 2.
videos.headline: Justice knocks down huge three off turnover
